### Template entry (delete me)

- **Root:** `config/default.yaml`
- **Copies:**
  - `config/prod.yaml` — production override; must have same keys
  - `docs/setup.md` — documents config; must match defaults
- **Re-check:** `diff <(yq . config/default.yaml) <(yq . config/prod.yaml)`
- **Last verified:** YYYY-MM-DD
- **Status:** SYNCED

### Agent context entry (delete me)

- **Root:** `CLAUDE.md` or `SOUL.md` (confirmed anchor for durable agent behavior)
- **Owner:** agent maintainer
- **Risk:** high — stale or conflicting agent context changes future tool choice and behavior
- **Copies:**
  - `skills/*/SKILL.md` — active skill contracts; must not contradict root instructions
  - `memory/` — durable facts; compact dated variants and preserve history when relevant
  - `session transcript` — transient heap; summarize durable decisions before compaction
- **Re-check:** `python scripts/mark.py --target . && python scripts/session_mark.py --target . --transcript <export>`
- **Last verified:** YYYY-MM-DD
- **Status:** NOT_CHECKED
